 {
   "id":"8064aaf9-6e35-49bf-b75a-ef81ae313213",
   "name":{
      "en":"Basic Programming"
   },
   "draft": false,
   "order": 4,
   "steps":[
      {
         "id":"a14a3e3f-ba52-4909-98f3-c38057eb2923",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"In this challenge you will learn about the basic program tools. To start, click on 'programs' card."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"601c6bb6-30ae-4e80-8e92-ca7eabb15d18",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Your tool list has four different categories: move, lights, sounds, and time."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"41c044f8-f859-446c-af3a-08d50ffcc81b",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"The 'move' card is the first in the list. By choosing blocks from this group, you can program your robot to move forward, backward, or turn. Click on the card and let's see the blocks."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"566a822a-09de-435e-b2df-042b87e50df3",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"With the first block you can program your robot to move forward."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"62aebbe9-d45a-4c2f-b45a-fb475ee00b30",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"You can do the same by choosing the next block, but for a longer period of time."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"2755825e-9bc7-4b44-8501-c953443ad7e5",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Choose the following block if you want your robot to move backward." 
           },      
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"c5df123d-9c8d-4a08-a71f-d989b8ac6ac8",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"By using the next block, your robot will move backward, but for a longer period of time."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"66bfe81d-0164-4da7-90e6-40f14270e27a",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Choose the following block if you want your robot to turn left."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"9f46bca1-cd7e-4de6-b579-554443137d1c",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"To turn right, tap on the next block."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },      {
         "id":"12996465-a46f-49fe-8916-c3ac90c76b9b",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"To program your robot to make a half-turn to the left, tap on the following block."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"0f984bc8-0cdf-4f43-944c-d6bbab43e9f4",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"And choose the last block if you want your robot to make a half-turn to the right."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"30922f4f-8fe7-484e-900e-fc8d436fe666",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"The next group of blocks is 'lights'. Here you can choose different color effects. Tap on its card to see your options."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
     {
         "id":"815f21af-ae1f-440f-a04c-b697badd92bb",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"By choosing the first block, you will add white light to your robot."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"05b0ae24-6025-41c6-9778-785eb50600a1",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"...or red..."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"fa228a15-2d9a-46c2-a22c-3a74fc19888a",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"...or green..."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"5348df73-1d5a-48d1-a363-981278e7cb2c",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"...or blue."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"f7da1058-0eb8-4f87-89da-a471747d8ea6",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"You can choose not to have any lights shown."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"2a90ea26-b92e-4d99-b925-697ee196985c",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"By choosing the next block, you robot will show red and blue colors, just like the police."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"6704802f-97cd-4cd6-bdd4-617af8ce5248",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"You can program your robot by adding rainbow colors as well."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"22d83707-b30d-4b74-b59c-341520ef87d2",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"You can even add the colors of a traffic light: red, yellow and green."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"fda6d770-50e1-4379-aca3-80380cba6e91",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Now let's check out the sound effects you can add to your robot. Click on the 'sounds' card."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"eee36303-5ecd-4f60-9d3c-7496f605c922",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Your robot can meow..."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"50ed87e0-210c-48fd-bba0-20a2e450162e",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"...or play monkey sounds."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },    
      {
         "id":"84fb45fe-43e4-422d-a12b-ee83891f7655",     
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"You can add robot sounds, too."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"6b17fd0e-bced-4fa6-8ca5-fce75c391791",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"And your robot can party as well!"
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"4139ccfb-333c-4dd1-9207-64c5e81eaa86",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Finally, let's click the 'time' card where you can add time breaks."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"ba72534b-3650-4220-bfe7-61b62662cc4e",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"By choosing the first block, you can add a 1-second-break."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"bfc254b8-af96-4111-ba05-b3cfd2b35a3a",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"You can also add a longer break that goes for 5 seconds, too."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"5b3a1a78-7335-4704-bf13-dcae6ecb79dc",
         "title":{
            "en":"Basic Programming"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Let's write a basic program together! Do the same flow that you can see on this screen then you can save it if you want."
         },
         "type":"vertical"
      },
      {
         "id":"4c4d3ddd-e752-4982-961c-cf5602fa826c",
         "title":{
            "en":"Good job!"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":""
         },
         "type":"zoomable"
      }
]
}